        "Open the meeting titled 'Potential Merger' in your Teams calendar — the Recap opens with AI Notes, chapters and action items. Click the Copilot icon in the top right of the Recap page — Copilot opens grounded in the transcript. Type: 'Format as a strategic-review minute with sections: Counterparty and Owner, Strategic Rationale Discussed, Concessions Offered, Concessions Received, Open Items, Approval Threshold, Next Step Owner and Date. Highlight any term that requires CFO sign-off in amber, and any term that requires Board sign-off in red.' Copy the result into a new Word document.",
