      tool(T_COWORK, FRONTIER_LIC, M365_ACCT, [
        "Open Cowork in M365 Copilot and paste this single prompt: 'Help me prepare in parallel for the Content Committee that closes the commissioning round in 30 days. Please do all 5 of the following at once and report back when each is ready: (1) draft a 2-page Word document titled \\'Content Committee Brief — ARPU and Compliance\\' using /ME_01_Content_Performance.xlsx, /ME_02_Content_Policy.docx and /ME_06_Content_Rights_Register.docx for context; (2) draft a second 1-page Word document titled \\'CEO Opening Statement\\' covering the 11% ARPU decline, the 28% content overrun, the 9% ad-revenue decline and the Kominfo/KPI/DJKI queries; (3) draft a confidential email to the Content Committee members with the meeting purpose, agenda and pre-read instructions; (4) schedule a 30-minute Teams prep meeting with the CCO, CFO and Head of Streaming for tomorrow at 7am for me to walk them through the deck before the Committee convenes; (5) post a discreet message in the Executive Committee Teams channel reminding members that all external communication is on hold until the Committee has met. Please confirm each task before sending external content.'",
        "Open Cowork in M365 Copilot and paste this single prompt: 'After the Content Committee has met, please complete in parallel: (1) draft the lender update email to our 3 relationship banks with the agreed messaging from the Committee minutes; (2) draft the regulator note for Kominfo, KPI and DJKI on the editorial, ad-volume and rights recovery programme; (3) create a 30-day finance leadership task list covering ARPU monitoring, ad-yield protection, content cost control, and title-by-title corrective actions, then send it to the FP&A, Treasury and Content Finance leads; (4) schedule a 20-minute checkpoint Teams meeting for this afternoon with the finance leadership team; (5) update the lender communication tracker workbook with today\\'s outreach. Wait for my confirmation before sending external emails.'"
      ], DESC_COWORK,
      promptsID=[
        "Buka Cowork di M365 Copilot dan tempelkan satu prompt ini: 'Bantu saya mempersiapkan secara paralel Komite Konten yang menutup putaran commissioning dalam 30 hari. Mohon kerjakan kelima hal berikut sekaligus dan laporkan begitu masing-masing siap: (1) susun dokumen Word 2 halaman berjudul \\'Briefing Komite Konten — ARPU dan Kepatuhan\\' menggunakan /ME_01_Content_Performance.xlsx, /ME_02_Content_Policy.docx dan /ME_06_Content_Rights_Register.docx sebagai konteks; (2) susun dokumen Word 1 halaman kedua berjudul \\'Naskah Pembukaan Direktur Utama\\' yang mencakup penurunan ARPU 11%, overrun konten 28%, penurunan pendapatan iklan 9%, dan pertanyaan Kominfo/KPI/DJKI; (3) susun email rahasia kepada anggota Komite Konten berisi tujuan rapat, agenda, dan instruksi pre-read; (4) jadwalkan rapat persiapan Teams 30 menit dengan Direktur Konten, Direktur Keuangan, dan Kepala Streaming besok pukul 07.00 untuk saya memandu mereka melalui deck sebelum Komite dimulai; (5) posting pesan diskret di channel Komite Eksekutif Teams yang mengingatkan bahwa semua komunikasi eksternal ditunda hingga Komite selesai. Mohon konfirmasi tiap tugas sebelum mengirim konten eksternal.'",
        "Buka Cowork di M365 Copilot dan tempelkan satu prompt ini: 'Setelah Komite Konten selesai, mohon kerjakan secara paralel: (1) susun email update kepada 3 bank relasi dengan pesan yang disepakati dari notulen Komite; (2) susun nota regulator untuk Kominfo, KPI, dan DJKI mengenai program pemulihan editorial, volume iklan, dan hak cipta; (3) buat task list 30 hari untuk leadership tim keuangan mencakup pemantauan ARPU, proteksi ad-yield, kontrol biaya konten, dan tindakan korektif per judul, kemudian kirimkan ke FP&A, Treasury, dan Content Finance; (4) jadwalkan rapat checkpoint Teams 20 menit sore ini bersama leadership tim keuangan; (5) perbarui workbook tracker komunikasi kreditor dengan outreach hari ini. Tunggu konfirmasi saya sebelum mengirim email eksternal.'"
      ],
      persona=['Indra Saputra', 'Budi Santoso'],
      personaID=['Indra Saputra', 'Budi Santoso']),

